'''轮胎平衡'''使质量在一个[[汽车|汽车]]车轮（包括[[轮胎|轮胎]]）中[[平衡|平衡]]分布，可分为静平衡和动平衡。动态不平衡会使车轮摇摆，令轮胎产生波浪型磨损；静态不平衡会产生颠簸和跳动现象，往往使轮胎产生平斑现象。 随着速度的增加，不平衡引起的震动会更明显<ref>{{cite web|title=动平衡|url=http://car.autohome.com.cn/shuyu/detail_25_26_540.html|website=汽车之家|accessdate=2016-11-02|archive-date=2021-05-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210503021251/https://car.autohome.com.cn/shuyu/detail_25_26_540.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。一般更换新轮胎时要做车轮动平衡<ref>{{cite web|title=车轮为什么要做动平衡 汽车高速抖动有关系吗？|url=http://auto.sohu.com/20151228/n432797736.shtml|website=搜狐汽车|publisher=汽车大师|accessdate=2016-11-02|date=2015-12-28|archive-date=2016-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161104004145/http://auto.sohu.com/20151228/n432797736.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
== 动平衡 ==
動平衡描述了當輪胎以高速旋轉時因質量不對稱分布而產生的力<ref>{{cite web|title=Wheel Balancing|url=http://www.aa1car.com/library/wheel_balancing.htm|website=AA1Car|accessdate=2016-11-02|archive-date=2021-05-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210503022516/https://www.aa1car.com/library/wheel_balancing.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。现有的传感器，如[[防抱死制动系统|防抱死制动系统]](ABS)、车轮速度[[传感器|传感器]]等可以实时检测轮胎不平衡。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Real-time Tire Imbalance Detection Using ABS Wheel Speed Sensors|author=Jianbo Lu, Dimitar Filev and Len Johnson|journal=AE Int. J. Mater. Manuf.|issue=1|doi=10.4271/2011-01-0981|year=2011|volume=4|pages=1036–1047}}</ref>
== 原理 ==
为减少车轮摆动，可在车轮的轮毂添加一个小重量。<ref>{{cite book|author1=Hatto Schneider|title=Auswuchttechnik|date=2003-05-06|publisher=Springer Berlin Heidelberg|url=https://books.google.de/books?id=X4q4kH4i78UC&pg=PA186&lpg=PA186&dq=wuchtzentrieren&source=bl&ots=uMwP-V6PH2&sig=LBS0pHPMoBGHQkokw6E3bsnA37s&hl=en&ei=tgSuSrGnLcPK_gaXp-jSBg&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q=wuchtzentrieren&f=false|accessdate=2016-11-02|archive-date=2021-05-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210503021309/https://books.google.de/books?id=X4q4kH4i78UC&pg=PA186&lpg=PA186&dq=wuchtzentrieren&source=bl&ots=uMwP-V6PH2&sig=LBS0pHPMoBGHQkokw6E3bsnA37s&hl=en&ei=tgSuSrGnLcPK_gaXp-jSBg&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q=wuchtzentrieren&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref>
== 环境影响 ==
传统上使用[[铅|铅]]做平衡块<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=r4fAAgAAQBAJ&pg=PT607|title=Today's Technician: Automotive Suspension & Steering Classroom Manual and Shop Manual|last=Schnubel|first=Mark|publisher=Cengage Learning|year=2014|isbn=9781305178410|page=607}}</ref><ref>[http://www.epa.gov/wastes/hazard/wastemin/nlfwwi.htm National Lead Free Wheel Weight Initiative (NLFWWI)] {{Wayback|url=http://www.epa.gov/wastes/hazard/wastemin/nlfwwi.htm |date=20150924143751 }}. epa.gov.</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=1bpxyxP1YSoC&pg=PA30&dq=tire+weights+lead&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwjNnK2Jq77MAhXCoD4KHWj9ASwQ6AEINDAA#v=onepage&q=tire%20weights%20lead&f=false|title=Postal Services pledges to remove 8,000 pounds of lead|date=2009-01|work=American Recycler|accessdate=3 May 2016|page=B2|archive-date=2021-05-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210503021323/https://books.google.com/books?id=1bpxyxP1YSoC&pg=PA30&dq=tire+weights+lead&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwjNnK2Jq77MAhXCoD4KHWj9ASwQ6AEINDAA#v=onepage&q=tire%20weights%20lead&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但因鉛具有[[毒性|毒性]]，欧洲在2002年6月通过法案，禁止用铅做动平衡<ref>[http://ak-bleifrei.izm.fraunhofer.de/servlet/is/2081/AnhangII_Altautorichtlinie_2002-6-27.pdf?command=downloadContent&filename=AnhangII_Altautorichtlinie_2002-6-27.pdf EU-Altfahrzeug-Verordnung] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160306183728/https://ak-bleifrei.izm.fraunhofer.de/servlet/is/2081/AnhangII_Altautorichtlinie_2002-6-27.pdf?command=downloadContent&filename=AnhangII_Altautorichtlinie_2002-6-27.pdf |date=2016-03-06 }}</ref>，而用含[[锌|锌]]或[[铜|铜]]的铅[[合金|合金]]或完全无铅的平衡块<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=hUoJAAAAQBAJ&pg=PA1167|title=Automotive Service: Inspection, Maintenance, Repair|last=Gilles|first=Tim|publisher=Cengage Learning|year=2012|isbn=9781133420682|page=1167}}</ref>。

